    "description": "Join the MT Educare family as a Curriculum Developer in Raipur. We believe in empowering our employees with the tools, training, and environment they need to succeed.\n\nAbout MT Educare:\nMT Educare is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Participate in school events, workshops, and training programs\n• Support students with special educational needs\n• Conduct doubt-clearing sessions and remedial classes for weak students\n• Maintain classroom discipline and create a positive learning environment\n• Coordinate with academic counselors for student career guidance\n• Utilize technology and digital tools to enhance learning outcomes\n• Contribute to school newsletter, blogs, and other publications\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Ed / M.Ed from a recognized institution\n• 12-20 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Lesson Planning\n• Proficiency in MS Office\n• Proficiency in LMS Platforms\n• Proficiency in Communication Skills\n• Proficiency in Content Creation\n• Proficiency in E-learning\n• Proficiency in IB Curriculum\n• Proficiency in Pedagogy\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Referral bonus program\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Employee stock options (ESOPs) for eligible roles\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Salary Range: 35 LPA - 70 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Raipur, Chhattisgarh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with MT Educare!",
